The paper proposes a novel method for multiview learning problem, which involves learning a classifier from multiple view data. This problem is commonly studied in the machine learning community, and the proposed method involves linear transformations, reconstruction, and classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves some natural language processing tasks, such as text classification, which could be categorized as cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper uses some multimedia data sets, which could be categorized as cs.MM (Multimedia).
